<tr id="L4"><td><a href="#L4">4</a></td><td>TORRES:  I'm approaching your position, but that ion storm blew out my deflector field. I've lost helm control and I'm venting plasma from the port nacelle.</td></tr>

<tr id="L5"><td><a href="#L5">5</a></td><td>CHAKOTAY [OC]:  We're modifying a tractor pulse to slow you down.</td></tr>

