<tr id="L8"><td><a href="#L8">8</a></td><td>JANEWAY [OC]:  Hold on, B'Elanna. This is going to be bumpy.</td></tr>

<tr id="L9"><td><a href="#L9">9</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The shuttlecraft bounces into the shuttlebay and skids to a halt. Not having any seatbelts, Torres lurches forward onto the console. Paris enters.</td></tr>

<tr id="L10"><td><a href="#L10">10</a></td><td>PARIS:  B'Elanna? Are you alive?</td></tr>

<tr id="L11"><td><a href="#L11">11</a></td><td>TORRES:  You tell me.</td></tr>

