<tr id="L151"><td><a href="#L151">151</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Torres is dragged along the deck to the helmsman.</td></tr>

<tr id="L152"><td><a href="#L152">152</a></td><td>KORTAR:  Is this the mongrel child you spoke of.</td></tr>

